MK309 Compile Commands

gcc -o MK309 MK309_Simulator.c `pkg-config --cflags --libs gtk+-3.0` -rdynamic -lm -lglut -lGLU -lGL

For OpenGL: 
gcc TacticalGraphics.c -o graphics -lglut -lGLU -lGL

gdb Debugger
-g

Anthing with <math.h> must include -lm

./MK309

MUST COMPILE AS C PROGRAM FOR GLADE RESOURCE FILE

Most up-to-date
gcc -g -o MK309 MK309_Simulator.c `pkg-config --cflags --libs gtk+-3.0` `pkg-config --cflags --libs epoxy` -rdynamic -lm -lglut -lGLU -lGL -lGLEW 
